messages.message: Is there a way in aihub build to edit a class of a document? It gets classified as "Other" but I want to manually change it to another class?
no, there is not. The only way to change a class would be to specifically add/edit your class prompts
The reason for this is that build should be representative of what the app results will be and re-assigning a document’s class will have no affect on the app run so it’s misleading to the user
hm ya, doing a more descriptive class worked
